column4: <content>Mariette & Bruegel. In Catal. Crozat, p. 106 reprinted as Ph. de Chennevières et A. de Montaiglon, Abecedario de P.J. Mariette, Tôme I, Paris, 1851, pp. 189f. where also Abecedario proper pp. 188-189. Mariette says ""celui que l'on nomme le vieux Breughel."" In Abecedario part already reference to Vasari...Bruegel never called drôle or peasant painter. To be reproduced from Crozat.</content>
